Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在眼中尚覺遙遠的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺已經來到面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並將迅速地成為回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「未來」的表情總是有點不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我們就用笑容去迎接她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 早安啊 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我試穿了制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有點高興而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也成為正式領航員了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就只有這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩要從領航員業界功成身退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱退的理由不只是那樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩好像很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就被邀請擔任鳳尾舟協會的常務理事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅侷限於亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是為了整個水上觀光業的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓她盡一份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 就算艾莉西亞前輩再怎麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法同時兼顧兩份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以好像請他們等到我成為正式領航員以後再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到結婚 其實我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定也是在等待我的晉級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我再認真一點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽…說艾莉西亞小姐要…要結婚是真的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我這是騙人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從早上開始就有一大堆人打電話來問這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是在哪裡聽到傳聞的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:16.36,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 嶄新的開端…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我熟悉工作之前 艾莉西亞前輩都會留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱退儀式全部都由協會來策劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣啦 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級擔心妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 藍華 愛麗絲 謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從知道艾莉西亞前輩要隱退那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就忙這忙那的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都忙得暈頭轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 艾莉西亞前輩總是面帶笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都仍舊和平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間像往常一樣流逝著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而又幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個數據是什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份文件…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…有份文件我不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到處在找妳哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人送花來給我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…都不希望艾莉西亞前輩隱退的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人也是…市民也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家其實都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡艾莉西亞前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是水之三大精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是很溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家的白雪公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想繼續跟妳在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚停不下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實在很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里就已經有能力成為正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我實在太害怕失去與燈里在一起的這段美好的時光…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己身為前輩必須要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我每次…每次都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都因為我太任性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太多的事情同時發生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這一切又太過幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是非常值得高興的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論時間或是空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在不斷變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為自己能夠理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但心中卻仍舊充滿不安與恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並肩走在一起時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺大家走的是同一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實大家都是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在探索著屬於自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走在自己的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有大家相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想要與在路的前方的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的未來邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得用笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來送走艾莉西亞前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長 今天也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個預約是庵野波平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來那是郵遞員叔叔的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天您不用上班嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我已經退休啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後就在辦公室做管理的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長久以來真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是蕎麥茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的稱號是海藍寶石嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到能坐在成為正式領航員的小妹妹的鳳尾舟上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一些交接工作的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩一直都陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…明天的隱退儀式結束以後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就真的變成一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有整個城鎮陪著小妹妹妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後透過郵遞員叔叔的介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天也有客人預約了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有幾位客人是佛洛林咖啡館的店長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(486,440)\fs20}Caffe Florian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鐘樓的管理員先生推薦來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在接受很多人的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里的亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經開張了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…亞利亞公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是騙人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉 你在哭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高興的眼淚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高興！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳成為正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到下雪的季節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 生奶油可可嗎？好久沒喝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要多多的奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩 超級任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦 核桃麵包久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剛剛出爐的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿了以前的所有…歡樂的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開這扇門 是我一天中的第一個工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在打開它 平凡的一天就即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這份溫馨的光景…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被冷冽的晨風吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將演繹出「現在」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 之後的大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中郵遞員伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近在上班前都會給我送來新鮮的雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他浮島的家中開始養雞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋的年輕分店長 藍華呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近開始有了威信 非常地帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只有我們兩個人在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是跟以前一樣是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說阿魯前段時間也成功晉級了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然最近不怎麼見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過藍華都會把他的近況詳細地告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說還長高了一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生也成功晉級了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是不知不覺出現在店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我覺得這一定是曉先生特有的關心方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好像很閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也到浮島來玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的跳級正式領航員愛麗絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是成為周圍目光的焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而愛麗絲最最熱衷的自我原則呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是三個人一塊去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不三個人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就會毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩受到大眾的推舉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段時間終於在歌劇院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召開了一場個人演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然愛麗絲抱怨她怠慢了領航員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過演唱會當天看到雅典娜前輩那身姿卻感動到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷哭了呢 要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋的晃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在名副其實地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為了光芒四射的No.1領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的身姿 真可謂是盛情綻放的薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 她總是礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要讓我的時代早日到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我知道她心裡肯定因為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃前輩的活躍而高興得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們永遠的白雪公主 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙著出席各式各樣的演講和典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集會和聯歡會等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都忙得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段時間我還看到了她與祖母一起擔任特邀講師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 在時間允許的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.23,0:22:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們又來看妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都像這樣 跟祖母一起來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有如水之精靈一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我們露出美麗的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被幸福包圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶來許多開端的風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果也能送到小愛那裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里前輩 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試穿了制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.45,0:24:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點高興罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.66,0:24:29.64,END,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445,469)\bord0\shad1\fsp6\3c&H475B5F&\4c&H575757&}願那起始之風  吹拂到您身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:37.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:47.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:57.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:08.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:13.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:20.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:27.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:37.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:51.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:04:00.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:37.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾記得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:47.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}湧上心頭的 感動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:57.74,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴著湛藍的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎風前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:08.87,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我陶醉時 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:13.59,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我們齊聲歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:20.71,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:27.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 嶄露頭角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.01,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}永遠地 充滿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:37.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}讓人陶醉的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:51.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}每個溫暖的 日子往復著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:04:00.06,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不經意間 從那遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}來到我身邊
